text:
My type of Mutton Briyani!  Taste excellent and generous portion of mutton at only $6.50.

Great varieties.

My empty plate is a good testimonial of how delicious it is, isn't it?

Chanced by this prata stall and gave it a try. Made on the spot, unlike usual prata stalls which have mountains of pre-made cold pratas at the side.
Prata was served hot, taste was quite ok, just that not crispy (-0.5 star) (might have to ask for more crisp). Vegetarian curry (Dal) was too watery (-0.5 star), thou taste wasn't too bad. I have tasted better pratas but this was decent.
Tastes of the food is beyond my expectations.. very well flavoured . The cook seems like a professional in bringing out authentic tastes . I highly recommend this food place to enjoy Ur food
My usual food place in jurong west, the 2 guys are friendly and give good service
